ta-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 09, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ujc1665702619229.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ujc1665702619229.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ujc1665702619229.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ujc1665702619229\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n               \n Uniface Reserved Words \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__uniface_reserved_words_530395\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Reserved words are terms that cannot be used to name your Rocket® Uniface objects.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__p_d177587e1_d177588e1_d177589e1\">The following words are reserved when naming any Uniface object:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__li_d54413e1_d54414e1_d54415e1\">Names of Repository entities.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__li_d54416e1_d54417e1_d54418e1\">Names of tables or files associated with Repository entities.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__li_d54419e1_d54420e1_d54421e1\">Names of overflow tables or files associated with\n            Repository entities. <p class=\"p\"></p><p class=\"p\">For more information about repository entities and all\n               tables and files associated with them, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qmx1665702737156.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qmx1665702737156.html\" title=\"The meta dictionary consists of modeled entities that describe the Uniface Repository itself. It is delivered as a file called umeta.xml in the uniface/misc directory of your installation. This file also includes some other database tables used by Uniface at runtime.\">Meta Dictionary</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__li_d54422e1_d54423e1_d54424e1\">Names of ProcScript statements, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tpi1665702624640.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tpi1665702624640.html\" title=\"The Uniface ProcScript language consists of a series of ProcScript statements that cause Uniface to perform specified actions, such as running a form, retrieving data, locking an occurrence, calling another ProcScript module, and so on.\">ProcScript: Statements</a> for details.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__li_d54425e1_d54426e1_d54427e1\">Names of ProcScript functions, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rfg1665702624715.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rfg1665702624715.html\" title=\"Refer to the topics under this section to understand functions related to ProcScript.\">ProcScript: Functions</a> for details. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">Names of ProcScript datatypes, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dld1665702530483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dld1665702530483.html\" title=\"Data types are classifications for data containers, such as fields, variables, parameters, and return values. They define the characteristics of the data and determine how the data is handled during processing and storage. Uniface has scalar data types and reference data types.\">Uniface Data Types</a> for details.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Names of ProcScript Precompiler Directives and Uniface Constants, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mlc1665702620662.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mlc1665702620662.html\" title=\"Precompiler directives and Uniface constants enable you to produce generalized, reusable ProcScript. They allow you to determine the exact composition of the ProcScript that will be compiled.\">ProcScript: Precompiler Directives and Uniface Constants</a> for details.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Anything considered by your DBMSs, networks, and operating systems to be a reserved\n            word. For details, and to validate syntax of names, see the appropriate documentation\n            for your systems.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Additionally, the following list of reserved words for naming specific repository\n               objects:<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"5\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__table_d18791e1_d18792e1_d18793e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Reserved Words for Naming Specific Repository Objects</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row valign-top\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__table_d18791e1_d18792e1_d18793e1__entry__1\">Entity </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__table_d18791e1_d18792e1_d18793e1__entry__2\">Modeled Field Interface </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__table_d18791e1_d18792e1_d18793e1__entry__3\">Modeled Field Layout </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__table_d18791e1_d18792e1_d18793e1__entry__4\">Modeled Field Syntax </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__table_d18791e1_d18792e1_d18793e1__entry__5\">Include ProcScript </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row valign-top\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry valign-top\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ujc1665702619229__table_d18791e1_d18792e1_d18793e1__entry__1\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__ul_yjg_wtz_whc\">\n<li class=\"li\">HEADER </li>\n<li class=\"li\">TRAILER </li>\n<li class=\"li\">UNIS </li>\n<li class=\"li\">*.APS </li>\n<li class=\"li\">*.DICT </li>\n<li class=\"li\">*.FRM </li>\n<li class=\"li\">*.PRINTER </li>\n<li class=\"li\">*.TEXT </li>\n<li class=\"li\">*.UGENERIC </li>\n<li class=\"li\">*.USYS</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry valign-top\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ujc1665702619229__table_d18791e1_d18792e1_d18793e1__entry__2\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__ul_hdn_g5z_whc\">\n<li class=\"li\">ATEST </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B193 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B194 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B195 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B196 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B197 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B198 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B199 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B200 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B201 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B202 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B203 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B204 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B205 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B206 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B207 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B208 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B209 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B210 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B211 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B212 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B220 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B221 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B221SEP </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B222 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B224 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B225 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B226 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B227 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B228 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B229 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B230 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">B231 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">DESCR </li>\n<li class=\"li\">EMPTY </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F1 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F128 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F16 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F192 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F2 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F3 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F31 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F32 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F4 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F6 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F64 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">F8 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">FIX40 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">PREFVAL </li>\n<li class=\"li\">STAMP </li>\n<li class=\"li\">TEXT </li>\n<li class=\"li\">TIMESTAMP </li>\n<li class=\"li\">UCOMMENT </li>\n<li class=\"li\">UDATE </li>\n<li class=\"li\">UTIME </li>\n<li class=\"li\">V2</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry valign-top\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ujc1665702619229__table_d18791e1_d18792e1_d18793e1__entry__3\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__ul_v4s_w5z_whc\">\n<li class=\"li\">DATE</li>\n<li class=\"li\">DATEDMY</li>\n<li class=\"li\">INV80</li>\n<li class=\"li\">NOINV340</li>\n<li class=\"li\">TESTD</li>\n<li class=\"li\">TIME</li>\n<li class=\"li\">TIMEHM</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry valign-top\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ujc1665702619229__table_d18791e1_d18792e1_d18793e1__entry__4\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__ul_zcz_tvz_whc\">\n<li class=\"li\">ACCNAM </li>\n<li class=\"li\">C3</li>\n<li class=\"li\">DISPROM </li>\n<li class=\"li\">DISPROMPT </li>\n<li class=\"li\">DTYP </li>\n<li class=\"li\">DTYPREG </li>\n<li class=\"li\">ENTITYNAME </li>\n<li class=\"li\">FIELDNAME </li>\n<li class=\"li\">FIELDNAMEKEY </li>\n<li class=\"li\">FLDNAME </li>\n<li class=\"li\">FORMNAMEKEY </li>\n<li class=\"li\">INHERIT </li>\n<li class=\"li\">LABEL </li>\n<li class=\"li\">LIBNAME </li>\n<li class=\"li\">LIBRNAME </li>\n<li class=\"li\">MAN2 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">MODELNAME </li>\n<li class=\"li\">MODELNAME0 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">NAME032 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">NAME16 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">NAME32 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">NOMANALL </li>\n<li class=\"li\">NUM2 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">NUMS3 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">NUMSX </li>\n<li class=\"li\">PRNUM </li>\n<li class=\"li\">SCHEMANAME </li>\n<li class=\"li\">SUBFLD </li>\n<li class=\"li\">TESTC3 </li>\n<li class=\"li\">TEXTLAN </li>\n<li class=\"li\">TEXTNAME </li>\n<li class=\"li\">YN </li>\n<li class=\"li\">YNB</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry valign-top\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ujc1665702619229__table_d18791e1_d18792e1_d18793e1__entry__5\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ujc1665702619229__ul_sgj_fwz_whc\">\n<li class=\"li\">DEFPARAM</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532706\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532706\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface Reserved Words Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 09, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface Reserved Words Reserved words are terms that cannot be used to name your Rocket® Uniface objects. The following words are reserved when naming any Uniface object: Names of Repository entities. Names of tables or files associated with Repository entities. Names of overflow tables or files associated with Repository entities. For more information about repository entities and all tables and files associated with them, see Meta Dictionary . Names of ProcScript statements, see ProcScript: Statements for details. Names of ProcScript functions, see ProcScript: Functions for details. Names of ProcScript datatypes, see Uniface Data Types for details. Names of ProcScript Precompiler Directives and Uniface Constants, see ProcScript: Precompiler Directives and Uniface Constants for details. Anything considered by your DBMSs, networks, and operating systems to be a reserved word. For details, and to validate syntax of names, see the appropriate documentation for your systems. Additionally, the following list of reserved words for naming specific repository objects: Table 1. Reserved Words for Naming Specific Repository Objects Entity Modeled Field Interface Modeled Field Layout Modeled Field Syntax Include ProcScript HEADER TRAILER UNIS *.APS *.DICT *.FRM *.PRINTER *.TEXT *.UGENERIC *.USYS ATEST B193 B194 B195 B196 B197 B198 B199 B200 B201 B202 B203 B204 B205 B206 B207 B208 B209 B210 B211 B212 B220 B221 B221SEP B222 B224 B225 B226 B227 B228 B229 B230 B231 DESCR EMPTY F1 F128 F16 F192 F2 F3 F31 F32 F4 F6 F64 F8 FIX40 PREFVAL STAMP TEXT TIMESTAMP UCOMMENT UDATE UTIME V2 DATE DATEDMY INV80 NOINV340 TESTD TIME TIMEHM ACCNAM C3 DISPROM DISPROMPT DTYP DTYPREG ENTITYNAME FIELDNAME FIELDNAMEKEY FLDNAME FORMNAMEKEY INHERIT LABEL LIBNAME LIBRNAME MAN2 MODELNAME MODELNAME0 NAME032 NAME16 NAME32 NOMANALL NUM2 NUMS3 NUMSX PRNUM SCHEMANAME SUBFLD TESTC3 TEXTLAN TEXTNAME YN YNB DEFPARAM Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}